## 📚 Concepts Covered

* Lexing / tokenization
* Parsing
* AST construction
* Tree-walking interpretation
* Environments & scope
* Expressions & statements
* Error handling

---

## 🎯 Learning Goals

This project helps you understand:

* How JavaScript engines work internally
* How compilers & interpreters differ
* How languages manage memory & scope
* How to design your own language

It’s the foundation for building:

* Compilers
* VMs
* Game scripting languages
* Custom DSLs
* AI scripting engines

